NK039(ti)012:0: ma mo dam ldan gyi lha mo rdo rje re
NK039(ti)012:1: ma ti'i dgyes bskyed ma chod sprin du spro ba'i
NK039(ti)012:2: thabs nyung ngur bsdus pa bzhugs so //
NK039(ti)012:3: na mo sh+r+ai gu ru we /
NK039(ti)012:4: 'dir ma mo'i mchod gsol bya bar 'dod pa dag gis gtor chen sha khrag gis brgyan pa dang /
NK039(ti)012:5: skyems phud dang gsur chen gyi dud pa dang bcas
NK039(ti)012:6: te rnal 'byor pas yi dam rgyun spyod kyi ngang
NK039(ti)012:7: la 'jug bzhin mchod rdzas rnams spel sbyangs kyi sngags
NK039(ti)012:11: ma rungs gdug pa'i bstan dgra'i gshed ma ru //
NK039(ti)012:12: ma cig bzang mo'i rnam rol ye shes kyi //
NK039(ti)012:13: ma mo dpal ldan lha mo re ma ti //
NK039(ti)012:14: ma thogs mchod pa'i gnas 'dir gshegs su gsol //
NK039(ti)012:15: ma bkod rang byung dgyes pa'i gdan la bzhugs //
NK039(ti)012:16: ma la dad dang gus pas phyag 'tshal te //
NK039(ti)012:17: ma tshogs mnyes byed mchod rdzas dngos bshams rnams //
NK039(ti)012:18: ma gtsang dris gos bsregs gtor bkrus sbyangs shing //
NK039(ti)012:19: ma yengs ting 'dzin sngags rgyas byin rlabs pa'i //
NK039(ti)012:20: ma 'dres phyi mchod chu gnyis nyer spyod lnga //
NK039(ti)012:21: ma spang nang gi 'dod yon tshogs dang gzhan //
NK039(ti)012:22: ma bcos byang chub sems kyi bdud rtsi sman //
NK039(ti)012:23: ma dag nyon mongs bsgral ba'i khrag chen po //
NK039(ti)012:24: ma h+aa mam sa'i gtor ma spungs pa bcas //
NK039(ti)012:25: ma dang mkha' 'gro rgya mtshor mchod par 'bul //
NK039(ti)012:26: ma khyod stong gsum dbang bsgyur gshegs tsam na //
NK039(ti)012:27: ma 'bad rdzu 'phrul stobs ldan shugs 'gro dang //
NK039(ti)012:28: ma yi yo byad rnam mang ji snyed pa //
NK039(ti)012:29: ma tshangs med pas nam mkha'i khams bkang nas //
NK039(ti)012:30: ma chen dpal ldan rdo rje lha mo ni //
NK039(ti)012:31: ma 'khor sprul pa yang sprul nying sprul gyi //
NK039(ti)012:32: ma sring 'khor bcas thugs dam bskang gyur cig /
NK039(ti)012:33: ma nor nges gsang snying po'i rnal 'byor la //
NK039(ti)012:34: ma 'gyangs mchog thun dngos grub sna tshogs stsol //
NK039(ti)012:35: ma thub ring nas brnags pa'i dgra bo rnams //
NK039(ti)012:36: ma shor da ltar bsgral ba'i gzugs phung tshogs //
NK039(ti)012:37: ma 'gags yangs pa'i zhal gyi hom khung du //
NK039(ti)012:38: ma bzhag da ltar rol cig dam ldan ma //
NK039(ti)012:39: ma rgyud yongs kyi gtso mo re ma ti //
NK039(ti)012:40: ma cig bu bzhin brtse gdung byams pa yi //
NK039(ti)012:41: ma g.yel rtag tu brten pa'i grogs mdzad phyir //
NK039(ti)012:42: ma bzod gdung ba'i dbyangs kyis bstod par bgyi //
NK039(ti)012:43: ma nyid ye shes spyan ldan rnal 'byor bdag /
NK039(ti)012:44: ma rig dbang gis 'gal 'khrul gyur pa kun //
NK039(ti)012:45: ma dmigs klong yangs zang thal chen po'i ngang //
NK039(ti)012:46: ma lus mthol zhing bshags so bzod par bzhes //
NK039(ti)012:47: ma gyur skyabs gcig gu ru'i dam bzhag las //
NK039(ti)012:48: ma 'da' ma 'da' rdo rje re ma ti //
NK039(ti)012:49: ma bor bdag cag dpon slob chab srid brtan //
NK039(ti)012:50: ma dros rgya mtsho'i 'jings las 'gran par mdzod //
NK039(ti)012:51: ces pa'ang dam ldan rdo rje'i lha mo'i mchod gsol
NK039(ti)012:52: sngar gshegs pa byang chub rgyal mtshan gyis mdzad pa
NK039(ti)012:53: las / ma 'ongs rnal 'byor bas kyang de bzhin mdzod /
NK039(ti)012:54: ces mthong ba dang yid la 'di ltar bya bar
NK039(ti)012:55: sems tshe ma mo dgyes pa'i mtshan ma nges par
NK039(ti)012:57: nges gsang snying po'i bstan gnas kahthoga rdo rje gdan
NK039(ti)012:58: gyi gtsug lag khang du sh+aakya'i ban sdom chos kyi
NK039(ti)012:59: rdo rjes rang lo bco brgyad par yi ger bkod
